{"tid":1685162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如大家發起個活動 就係一齊幫自己果區侯選人做文宣/派傳單","createTime":"2019-10-31T11:44:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T12:06:08.000Z","uid":320737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b789c6e7638973553edab742a27563a2db99d952","tid":1685162,"uid":320737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:44:42.000Z","msg":"唔好意思我真係忍唔住<br />\n我呢幾日返屋企都見到自己果區既黃色侯選人 自己一個係度派傳單 個心真係好撚痛 點解會人幫佢<br />\n佢仲要要打低係呢個區紮根左二十年 民意一定唔低既周永勤 同時仲有何軍妖派左個助手落黎扮黃想𠝹佢票<br />\n我自己就主動飛屎卜pm聯絡左林進 準備幫佢手做文宣<br />\n如果大家想贏 大家一齊出一分力 幫自己果區既侯選人做下文宣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下你地 因為今次真係一輸就玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd01e30ea8726952b0712576f827a35c2646165","tid":1685162,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:45:40.000Z","msg":"（公投）11.2好似有活動撞左時間<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1685128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1685128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n入嚟幫手推下討論下投票啦手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c6beacc66d6868cc7bfd6232d249a58c386722","tid":1685162,"uid":178066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:48:48.000Z","msg":"推 屯門友"},{"pid":"8bcf84d3d48680bee5bab77d785bbd1d0bc359cb","tid":1685162,"uid":252064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T12:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JdEYeKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJdEYeKY.jpg&h=8229b038&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}